	<center>
		<form>
		<h3>提供社群資料<br></h3>
		<h5>如果提供，信用等級會提高<br></h5>
		<table class="table table-bordered myTbody" style = "width:80%">
			<tr>
				<td style = "width:20%">購物平台</td>
	    			<td><img src = "/images/yahoo.png" style = "width:30px"> <img src = "/images/lu.png" style = "width:30px">
	    			<button type="button" class="btn btn-default btn-sm">
	    			<span class="glyphicon glyphicon-plus" aria-hidden="true"></span>添加</button></td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td style = "width:20%">社群平台</td> 
	    			<td><img src = "/images/fbicon.png" style = "width:30px"> <img src = "/images/twit.png" style = "width:30px"> 
	    			<img src = "/images/in.png" style = "width:30px"> <button type="button" class="btn btn-default btn-sm">
	    			<span class="glyphicon glyphicon-plus" aria-hidden="true"></span>添加</button></td>
			</tr>
		</table>
		<br>
		<h4>
			E-mail認證信已寄往您所填寫的地址：
			<br>
			<span class="red"><%=email%></span>
			<br>
			您可於一小時內前往您的信箱點擊連結進行認證或於個人檔案頁面重發認證信
		</h4>
		<br>
		<button type="button" class="btn btn-default btn-lg" onClick = "javascript:location.href='/signup/_success'" >
		  <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-ok" aria-hidden="true"></span> 確認
		</button>
		<button type="button" class="btn btn-default btn-lg" onClick = "javascript:location.href='/signup/_success'" >
		  <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-play" aria-hidden="true"></span> 略過
		</button>
